| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2192 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 35a62dd8-2b6d-5dd9-b694-6ad8711fc996"
